author: @irunclasseu
text: MY TAEYONG!!!!! 💚💚💚 You will never know but you 'saved' me a lot of times this day. I had one of my worst days today, had my anxiety attacks triggered really bad and I was struggling so much earlier but suddenly, out of nowhere in the midst of breaking down, I got a notification that my SHALALA album arrived without expecting it at all. Once I had calmed down, went straight to receive my package and unboxed. I was so down but became soooo happy pulling out my desired photo card of you and seeing all your photos in the album. You made me really happy! And as I am remembering what happened today, you dropped this music video. I am feeling even better, much better than I thought. I love you so much! I have been a tyongf for 5 years already and I have always felt like you're a friend that gives me comfort without having to actually talk to you. Thank you and I love you today as well, and always, TAEYONG. 🥺💚
